import {
    Wrapper,
    Card,
    FieldWrapper,
    DescHeader,
    Description,
    TuitionRow,
    TuitionLabel,
    TuitionValue
} from './ProgramInfo.styles'


const ProgramInfo = ({programDescription, schoolDescription, schoolName}) => (
    <Wrapper>
        <FieldWrapper>
            <DescHeader>Earn Your Degree</DescHeader>
            <Description>{programDescription}</Description>
            <DescHeader>About {schoolName}</DescHeader>
            <Description>{schoolDescription}</Description>
        </FieldWrapper>
        <Card>
            <DescHeader center>Tuition Breakdown</DescHeader>
            <TuitionRow>
                <TuitionLabel>Cost per credit</TuitionLabel>
                <TuitionValue style={{marginLeft: "auto"}}>$46</TuitionValue>
            </TuitionRow>
            <hr></hr>
        </Card>
    </Wrapper>
)

export default ProgramInfo
